text: Esko Hillebrandt (born 20 April 1962) is a Finnish rower. He competed in the men's double sculls event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1962 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Finland Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Imatra
